Method Detail

showDialog

public int showDialog()
Display the dialog box, locks this thread while the dialog is being displayed, and returns a hashtable of data field values when the user closes the dialog box. Use this instead of Dialog.show(). If Hashtable returned is null, then the cancel button was clicked. Otherwise, it will contain a hash of labels(String) to results (Object).

Returns:
HashTable of labels to values
